" Abbreviations for specific filetypes only
" LaTeX
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> < \textless
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> > \textgreater
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> 19th 19$^{th}$
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> 18th 18$^{th}$
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> 17th 17$^{th}$
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> 16th 16$^{th}$
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> 20th 20$^{th}$
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> 21st 21$^{st}$
autocmd FileType tex :iabbrev <buffer> zz \\
" Python
autocmd FileType python :iabbrev <buffer> iff if:<left>


